                        Front End Developer
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        Create stunning user interfaces for the web. Flexible hours.
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p class="text-error">Not accepting applications</p>
                    </td>
                </tr> -->
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

</body>

</html>